{"tid":2498463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英與李柱銘何俊仁就8.18案上訴 就定罪及刑期申請上訴許可","createTime":"2021-04-21T07:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:49:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"753a04a459676598c0cbda30b0d4a85ca8745c63","tid":2498463,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5801&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=785e5baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5801</a><br />\n<br />\n黎智英囚14個月 8.31案求減刑 與李柱銘何俊仁就8.18案上訴定罪<br />\n<br />\n【東方日報】上周五(16日)黎智英分別就前年8.18日及8.31的2宗未經批准集結案，被判合共入獄14個月。而8.18案中另外2名被告何俊仁及李柱銘則被判緩刑。3人昨日(20日)分別就8.18案提出上訴，要求撤銷定罪及減刑；而黎智英同時就8.31案提出減刑申請。<br />\n<br />\n他們現同時就8.18案件被定罪以及判刑提出上訴。在此案中，黎智英被判即時監禁12個月，李柱銘被判監11個月但緩刑2年，何俊仁則被判監12個月但緩刑2年。<br />\n<br />\n至於8.31之案件，黎智英在此案被判即時監禁8個月，其中2個月刑期與8.18案的刑期分期執行。他現在亦就此案的判刑提出上訴。司法機構暫時仍未就這2宗上訴案安排聆訊日期。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20210421新聞 #0818維園 #0831灣仔"},{"pid":"ab4a8b83051a40cbaf04eb307e0946af82a741f1","tid":2498463,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f661eea1abf18b4db9ca2f287c1ed08f7542dd","tid":2498463,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:51:41.000Z","msg":"上訴咪姐係上訴庭"},{"pid":"9ae56a255f01343a1dd97fc001f8246feefecb4a","tid":2498463,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2aa787ce59db052649348fd799bf7afbd71dab","tid":2498463,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f661eea1abf18b4db9ca2f287c1ed08f7542dd","tid":2498463,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:51:41.000Z","msg":"上訴咪姐係上訴庭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"就算上到終審其實一樣無用<br />\n李義都投左共好耐"},{"pid":"5c12bc3bc6f5af4beaf4f5ec42538fb1fcb1fa69","tid":2498463,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}